metadata.name: Trace of things experienced
metadata.description:
Participation token of the immersive multimedia installation on the main stange of NFC Lisbon 2023. 

 The project delves into the theme of identity and privacy in the age of social media, blockchain and artificial intelligence. It serves as a provocative reflection of our contemporary society, one that is perpetually under the omnipresence of recording devices, pervasive data collection systems, and persistent digital footprints. 

 Ivona Tau
